<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有心嘅就算唔係關愛座都會讓<br />\n根本個問題係有好多人攞關愛座黎審判人<br />\n一有後生仔/冇需要嘅人坐關愛座就會比人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ab88034710ab55b142269d61a6c9af729fe0f2","tid":36444,"uid":21,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"矛盾只因關愛座 坐得嗎<br />\n常期望有空位坐剩 然後抖下<br />\n你問我做乜唔hub下 怕老人睥嘛<br />\n痛定思痛 廢柴 企吧<br />\n回頭看咁多關愛座 淨翻低<br />\n竟會沒呀嬸埋位<br />\n當佢仍然未想坐<br />\n就讓我先坐吧<br />\n這個決定多麼錯<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因關愛座<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/29045?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/29045?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ad19fd38771b9c3b86adfe6182d3f4d5142425b","tid":36444,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾專用座</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢老專用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得罪你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢老唔企得就咪出街 番老人院訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e40b2f073b1d6e0289f1201b42d286f50e6d726","tid":36444,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇理， 平時搭地鐵不論係唔係關愛座都唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我總站都唔會坐"},{"pid":"f68ca1e360e6976b00240997bb99109ed84199c4","tid":36444,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇理， 平時搭地鐵不論係唔係關愛座都唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /