r />\n呢啲人真係早啲死好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92907bb6a12d4dd67aa7df09c0dbfb19d6632876","tid":36444,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T21:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關愛座：平時會對身邊的人好熱情 但其實內心十分孤獨 很需要人額外的關心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我本身預啲人咁回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dcf72c97fc916b131f0823f310cce7435e81d1","tid":36444,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T21:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇理， 平時搭地鐵不論係唔係關愛座都唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我總站都唔會坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但有時m到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有需要都唔敢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪傻仔囉"},{"pid":"02c9ecebbc2235f0b47c3cef1b54d903e9e0dd0d","tid":36444,"uid":63721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T23:53:18.000Z","msg":"我會照坐<br />\n平時全個車廂都係打工族，學生哥 但冇人敢坐真係好on9 咁個位吉左出黎 浪費哂<br />\n有冇諗過啲傷殘/智障坐左關愛左更加會俾人歧視？<br />\nBtw見到老人家 傷殘/智障人士 我會讓位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5d93ed8ea47327a78bc80626cf25f4a26c0f7d","tid":36444,"uid":53089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會照坐<br />\n平時全個車廂都係打工族，學生哥 但冇人敢坐真係好on9 咁個位吉左出黎 浪費哂<br />\n有冇諗過啲傷殘/智障坐左關愛左更加會俾人歧視？<br />\nBtw見到老人家 傷殘/智障人士 我會讓位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解，呢幾日胃痛到癲都坐左，最多望下有冇